title: Aquazone 1.5
description:
Full version of Aquazone v1.5, it contains a full, untouched ISO of the install disc, along with all of my old fish and item files that I could find, some from websites that no longer exist!

There are also two Guppy System zip files, I believe those can be used to upgrade to the guppy version, but I have to boot one of my older computers to verify. I've included Discus, Arowana, and loads of other assorted files from my days using this.

Have fun y'all
